<template>
  <v-container 
    fluid
    class="pa-2">
    <v-card>
      <TopCardButtons />
        <v-card-title>
            Dashboard
        </v-card-title>
        <v-card-subtitle
          class="pb-0">
            <v-breadcrumbs 
            :items="items" 
            class="pl-0 pt-0 ">
                <template v-slot:divider class="breadPadZero">
                    <v-icon>mdi-chevron-right</v-icon>
                </template>
            </v-breadcrumbs>
        </v-card-subtitle>
    </v-card>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import TopCardButtons from './Buttons/TopCardButtons.vue'

export default {
    data: () => ({
      items: [
        {
          text: 'SalesCore',
          disabled: false,
          href: 'breadcrumbs_dashboard',
        },
        {
          text: 'AFR',
          disabled: false,
          href: 'breadcrumbs_link_1',
        },
        {
          text: 'Przychody & GP',
          disabled: true,
          href: 'breadcrumbs_link_2',
        },
      ],
    }),
    components: {
      TopCardButtons
    }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

.breadPadZero {
  padding: 0 !important;
}

</style>
